cow
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an unpleasant or wretched person, animal, thing, or situation, often preceded by an intensifying, often depreciatory epithet fair; dirty, rotten, silly etc., and often used good-humouredly
